N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 21.6 - Person

State Regulations

Person means any individual, partnership, corporation, association or other business unit, and shall be deemed to include broker, agent, cooperative corporation and unincorporated cooperative
association. Notes
